## Backend API Reference (Complete Endpoint Map)

### Auth — `/api/auth`
| Method | Endpoint | Request Body | Response | Used By |
|--------|----------|-------------|----------|---------|
| POST | `/auth/signup` | `{ name, email, password }` | `{ token, user }` | `SignUp.tsx` |
| POST | `/auth/login` | `{ email, password }` | `{ token, user }` | `Login.tsx` |
| POST | `/auth/google` | `{ idToken }` | `{ token, user }` | `SignUp.tsx`, `Login.tsx` |
| POST | `/auth/forgot-password` | `{ email }` | `{ message }` | `Login.tsx` (modal) |
| POST | `/auth/reset-password` | `{ token, newPassword }` | `{ message }` | Future: ResetPassword page |
| GET | `/auth/me` | — | `{ user + subscription }` | `useAuthStore` (on app load) |

### User — `/api/users`
| Method | Endpoint | Request Body | Response | Used By |
|--------|----------|-------------|----------|---------|
| GET | `/users/profile` | — | `{ user + subscription }` | `Profile.tsx` |
| PATCH | `/users/profile` | `{ name?, avatarUrl? }` | `{ user }` | `Profile.tsx` |
| PATCH | `/users/onboarding` | `{ isOnboarded: true }` | `{ user }` | `Onboarding.tsx` |

### Scans — `/api/scans`
| Method | Endpoint | Request Body | Response | Used By |
|--------|----------|-------------|----------|---------|
| POST | `/scans` | `FormData { image, restaurantName? }` | `{ scan: { id, status } }` | `UploadMenu.tsx` |
| GET | `/scans` | Query: `?search=&page=&limit=` | `{ scans[], total, page }` | `ScanHistory.tsx` |
| GET | `/scans/recent` | — | `{ scans[] }` (last 3) | `Dashboard.tsx` |
| GET | `/scans/:id` | — | `{ scan + counts }` | `ProcessingMenu.tsx`, `MenuResults.tsx` |
| GET | `/scans/:id/dishes` | Query: `?vegStatus=&badge=&sort=&page=&limit=` | `{ dishes[], total }` | `MenuResults.tsx` |
| GET | `/scans/:id/dishes/:dishId` | — | `{ dish }` | `DishDetails.tsx` |
| GET | `/scans/:id/recommendations` | — | `{ recommendations[] }` | `MenuResults.tsx`, `Dashboard.tsx` |
| PATCH | `/scans/:id` | `{ restaurantName }` | `{ scan }` | `ScanHistory.tsx` (rename) |
| DELETE | `/scans/:id` | — | `{ message }` | `ScanHistory.tsx` (soft delete) |

### Subscription — `/api/subscription`
| Method | Endpoint | Request Body | Response | Used By |
|--------|----------|-------------|----------|---------|
| GET | `/subscription` | — | `{ subscription }` | `Profile.tsx`, `Dashboard.tsx` |
| GET | `/subscription/usage` | — | `{ scansUsed, scansLimit, remaining, isUnlimited }` | `Dashboard.tsx`, `UploadMenu.tsx` |
| GET | `/subscription/success` | Query: `?session_id=` | `{ subscription }` | Stripe redirect callback |
| POST | `/subscription/checkout` | — | `{ url }` (Stripe checkout URL) | `Upgrade.tsx` |
| POST | `/subscription/portal` | — | `{ url }` (Stripe portal URL) | `Profile.tsx` |

