> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Route changes required:** Several routes need dynamic params now:
> - `/processing` → `/processing/:scanId` (so we know which scan to poll)
> - `/results` → `/results/:scanId` (so we know which scan's dishes to fetch)
> - `/dish/:id` → `/dish/:scanId/:dishId` (need both IDs for the API call)

