- Get `scanId` and `dishId` from URL params
- Use `useDishDetail(scanId, dishId)` for all dish data
- Remove `import { allItems } from "@/data/mockData"`
- Map API field names to display:
  - `dish.vegStatus` (`VEG`/`NON_VEG`) → Vegetarian/Non-Vegetarian badge
  - `dish.healthBadge` (`HEALTHY`/`MODERATE`/`AVOID`) → status badge
  - `dish.healthScore` → score display
  - `dish.ingredients` (JSON array) → ingredient chips
  - `dish.cookingStyle` → cooking style chips
  - `dish.healthReason` → "Why we rated it" section
  - `dish.bestFor` (comma-separated string) → split into list
  - `dish.avoidIf` (comma-separated string) → split into list
- Show loading skeleton while fetching

