**Changes:**
- Use `useScanHistory(searchTerm, page)` hook for data
- Remove `useState` for `history` — data comes from TanStack Query
- Search → becomes a debounced query param (not local filter)
- Delete → calls `useDeleteScan().mutate(id)` → TanStack auto-refetches list
- Rename → calls `useRenameScan().mutate({ id, restaurantName })` via a dialog
- "View Analysis" button → navigate to `/results/${scan.id}` (not static `/results`)
- Show pagination controls if total > 12
- Loading skeletons while fetching
- Remove `import { mockScanHistory } from "@/data/mockData"`

