## Data Flow Diagram — Complete

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant Z as Zustand Store
    participant TQ as TanStack Query
    participant AX as Axios (API Client)
    participant BE as Hono Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over U,DB: LOGIN FLOW
    U->>AX: POST /auth/login {email, pw}
    AX->>BE: Forward request
    BE->>DB: Find user, verify password
    DB-->>BE: User + Subscription
    BE-->>AX: { token, user, subscription }
    AX-->>Z: setAuth(token, user, subscription)
    Z-->>U: isAuthenticated=true → redirect /dashboard

    Note over U,DB: SCAN FLOW
    U->>AX: POST /scans (FormData: image)
    AX->>BE: Upload image (JWT in header)
    BE->>DB: Create scan (PENDING)
    BE-->>AX: { scan: { id, status: PENDING } }
    AX-->>U: Navigate to /processing/:scanId

    loop Poll every 2s
        TQ->>AX: GET /scans/:scanId
        AX->>BE: Check status
        BE-->>AX: { scan: { status: PROCESSING|COMPLETED } }
        TQ-->>U: Update progress UI
    end

    Note over U,DB: VIEW RESULTS
    TQ->>AX: GET /scans/:id/dishes?sort=healthiest
    AX->>BE: Fetch dishes
    BE->>DB: Query DishResult + filters
    DB-->>BE: Dishes array
    BE-->>AX: { dishes, total }
    TQ-->>U: Render dish cards with real data
```

