## Verification Plan

### Per-Phase Checks

| Phase | Test |
|-------|------|
| ① API Client | `api.get('/health')` returns `{ status: "ok" }` in browser console |
| ② Auth Store | After login, `useAuthStore.getState()` shows token + user in devtools |
| ③ Firebase | Google popup appears, ID token logged to console |
| ④ Auth Pages | Signup → login → redirects to dashboard. Google login works. Forgot password sends email |
| ⑤ Scan Flow | Upload real menu photo → processing polls → results show AI-analyzed dishes with health scores |
| ⑥ Dashboard | Shows latest scan data. History loads paginated scans. Search works. Delete removes scan |
| ⑦ Profile | Shows real user name/email. Upgrade redirects to Stripe. Manage Billing redirects to portal |
| ⑧ Cleanup | `npm run build` succeeds. No imports from `mockData.ts`. No TypeScript errors |

### End-to-End Flow (Final Verification)

1. **Fresh user:** Visit `/` → click "Get Started" → `/signup` → create account → `/onboarding`
2. **First scan:** `/onboarding` → "Upload First Menu" → `/upload` → upload image → `/processing/:id` → auto-redirect to `/results/:id` → see AI results
3. **Explore results:** Filter by Veg, sort by healthiest, click dish → `/dish/:scanId/:dishId` → see full detail
4. **Scan limit:** Hit 3 scan limit → shows upgrade banner → click "Upgrade" → Stripe checkout → complete → Pro user → unlimited scans
5. **History:** `/history` → see all past scans → search → rename → delete
6. **Profile:** `/profile` → see real data, manage billing, log out
7. **Return visit:** Close browser → reopen → JWT auto-loads from localStorage → `/dashboard` shows data without re-login

